<paragraph id="A98259D769306D99068C8FF5C1E684C8" pageId="0" pageNumber="125">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="CE12B0F31B129C4B0862E983B27345FC" pageId="0" pageNumber="125">
Algeria: Lac Tonga, surroundings of Lacalle [= El Kala]; Djurdjura; Annaba [= 
<normalizedToken id="E533BA698D42B34D257361F9B614D4C3" originalValue="Bône">Bone</normalizedToken>
] (
<bibRefCitation id="3CD76B23D2B5A8A4FDBDC77AF9911491" author="Lucas, PH" journalOrPublisher="Imprimerie Nationale, Paris" pageId="0" pageNumber="125" publicationUrl="https://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/page/46117987" refId="B14" refString="Lucas, PH, 1849. Histoire Naturelle des Animaux Articules. Deuxieme Partie. Insectes. Exploration scientifique de L'Algerie pendant les Annees 1840, 1841, 1842. Sciences Physiques. Zoologie II. Imprimerie Nationale, Paris, https://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/page/46117987" title="Histoire Naturelle des Animaux Articules. Deuxieme Partie. Insectes. Exploration scientifique de L'Algerie pendant les Annees 1840, 1841, 1842. Sciences Physiques. Zoologie II." url="https://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/page/46117987" year="1849">Lucas 1849</bibRefCitation>
