<subSubSection id="AF41A59226A6445292FC35B99EFF67F4" pageId="0" pageNumber="125" type="ecological data">
<paragraph id="AB2D7CF14C14C4F2CCBDC564CDF02E4C" pageId="0" pageNumber="125">Ecological data.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="BAED6031FE204205BF7284F4A9B85E4C" pageId="0" pageNumber="125">
The only data available on the host plants of 
<taxonomicName id="DAEE5B838F65CAAD7CB7C8B4393F0932" genus="B." lsidName="B. violacea" pageId="0" pageNumber="125" rank="species" species="violacea">
<emphasis id="5F8C62BF623A506DD5F6661031FC2AE1" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="125">B. violacea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
are by 
<bibRefCitation id="003A6DBDB80E2802B97C9E946D4D0ECB" author="Jolivet, P" journalOrPublisher="Bulletin de la Societe des Sciences naturelles et Physiques du Maroc" pageId="0" pageNumber="125" pagination="305 - 394" refId="B12" refString="Jolivet, P, 1967. Notes systematiques et ecologiques sur les Chrysomelides Marocains (Coleoptera) (2e note). Bulletin de la Societe des Sciences naturelles et Physiques du Maroc 1966: 305 - 394" title="Notes systematiques et ecologiques sur les Chrysomelides Marocains (Coleoptera) (2 e note)." volume="1966" year="1967">Jolivet (1967</bibRefCitation>
, as 
<taxonomicName id="FF8E2D11B2ED37E49977EEC5FC4D0C1E" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Galeruca" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Galeruca violacea" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="125" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="violacea">
<emphasis id="85565C8397656634A79CA491431826C1" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="125">Galeruca violacea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
): 
<taxonomicName id="C373DF47567CDC4087E95D6E70303388" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Pulicaria" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Pulicaria odora" order="Asterales" pageId="0" pageNumber="125" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="odora">
<emphasis id="88F525E1F8180CE315C5CCF5160D969D" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="125">Pulicaria odora</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
L. (
<taxonomicName id="23D016390F2FB7841AB41BF3EE8308B6" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Pulicaria" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="" order="Asterales" pageId="0" pageNumber="125" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="family">Asteraceae</taxonomicName>
), 
<taxonomicName id="9E851CBC3A6B0FDDCA3D5125AC0A73C3" class="Dicotyledoneae" family="Polygonaceae" genus="Rumex" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Rumex acetosella subsp. angiocarpus" order="Polygonales" pageId="0" pageNumber="125" phylum="Angiospermae" rank="subSpecies" species="acetosella" subSpecies="angiocarpus">
<emphasis id="43D6594E587D346106E285EDD262074B" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="125">Rumex acetosella angiocarpus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Murb. and 
<taxonomicName id="833CA7352DB5B19D20F1EA5C9802DCA3" class="Dicotyledoneae" family="Polygonaceae" genus="Rumex" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Rumex scutatus subsp. induratus" order="Polygonales" pageId="0" pageNumber="125" phylum="Angiospermae" rank="subSpecies" species="scutatus" subSpecies="induratus">
<emphasis id="3EC3E735740AAE6A2DF8ECF0AB445D2B" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="125">Rumex scutatus induratus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Boissier (
<taxonomicName id="4471B4AA3B0159DCAC53DDCB37BD70DA" class="Dicotyledoneae" family="Polygonaceae" genus="Rumex" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="" order="Polygonales" pageId="0" pageNumber="125" phylum="Angiospermae" rank="family">Polygonaceae</taxonomicName>
). However, these data require future confirmation.
</paragraph>
